description:
TUE 8/30 - Comedian/actor Hannibal Buress begrudgingly visits his "friends" at The Breakfast Club as they grill him on his career ever since taking down Bill Cosby with his stand-up bit, why he threw $26 at a fan while eating chicken wings, and why Beyonce pointed at him while Jay Z had to tell him to "be cool".
